summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to land use and zoning; amending Plat 21E, page 74, and Plat 22W, page 75 of the Official Land Use Map to rezone certain property described as Lots 1-7, block 13, Pallatine Hills Addition, and Lots 16-30, Block 7, sunset Heights Addition and located generally between North 42nd and North 43rd Street along Greenwood Avenue North from Single Family Attached (SFA) Zone to Residential Single Family 5000 (SF 5000) Zone. (Petition of Timothy Muir; C.F. 296075).
